bilingual.source: Her inability prevented her from completing the task.
bilingual.target: 她的无力让她无法完成这项任务。

bilingual.source: His inability cost him the advantage in the competition.
bilingual.target: 他的无力让他在比赛中失去了优势。

bilingual.source: His inability to cope with stress made him very frustrated.
bilingual.target: 无力应对压力让他感到非常沮丧。

bilingual.source: The inability to concentrate affected her performance at work.
bilingual.target: 她无力集中注意力影响了她的工作表现。

bilingual.source: Due to his inability to pay tuition, he had to drop out.
bilingual.target: 由于无力支付学费，他不得不辍学。

bilingual.source: The inability to pay the bills on time caused a lot of stress.
bilingual.target: 无力按时支付账单带来了很多压力。

bilingual.source: He felt a deep sense of inability to change the situation.
bilingual.target: 他感到一种深深的无力，无法改变现状。

bilingual.source: Due to his inability to drive, he had to rely on public transportation.
bilingual.target: 由于他无力驾驶，他不得不依赖公共交通。

bilingual.source: You can also talk to your creditor and explain him your inability to repay the loan.
bilingual.target: 您还可以与你的债权人，并解释他的无力偿还贷款。

bilingual.source: I do not know what I have to, the inability loss in the chaotic world of wandering.
bilingual.target: 我不知道我要什么，彷徨无力的在这个混沌的世界里徘徊。

yingyinNormal.en: And your bad jokes and your complete inability to ever hide a single thing you felt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有蹩脚的笑话，和你不懂掩饰自己的每一丝情感。

yingyinNormal.en: Cancer is basically an inability of the body to control the speed at which cells divide.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从根本上来说，癌症是身体缺乏调节细胞分裂速度能力的体现。

yingyinNormal.en: No, we were annihilated by our own incompetence and the inability of some people to follow the chain of command.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，我们的惨败是源于我们自己的无能，以及某些人没有能够听从指挥。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, both selective mutism and an inability to separate from one's mother can stem from a pathological fear of women.
yingyinNormal.zh: 无论是选择性缄默症还是无法离开母亲独自生活，都可能是源于对女性的病理性恐惧。

yingyinNormal.en: The right sleeve of your jacket, plus the formaldehyde mixed with your cologne and your complete inability to stop looking at your watch.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你夹克的右袖子。而且你的古龙水混着福尔马林的味道，还有你完全无法忍住不看表。

yingyinNormal.en: This change creates the intense experience of happiness, feeling social, increased empathy and the inability to sleep, which is likely why it is such a popular party drug.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个改变让人感到极度开心，变得爱交朋友，有同理心，亢奋到睡不着，这也是摇头丸为何成为受欢迎的派对必备药物。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2015-2022年全国卷高考试卷，包括阅读、完形、单选、填空、听力、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2015-2022年8年间全国卷和自主命题省市高考卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
